<aka>Touch Your people</aka>
<key>E</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Herre, møt Ditt folk igjen,
 med Din sterke allmakts hånd, vi ber
 La Ditt rike skinne her på jord,
 ved din Brud som tror Ditt Ord.
 Ikke for et kort behov,
 ved Din kraft; en indre fred - vi tror.
 La et mektig stormvær komme nå,
 Herre, møt Ditt folk igjen.

[V2]
 Chorus
 Kor: Touch Your people once again,
 with Your precious holy hand, I pray;
 let Your Kingdom shine upon this earth,
 through a wonderous, glorious bride.
 Not for temporary deeds,
 but to restore authority and power.
 Let a rushing mighty wind blow,
 touch Your people once again.

[V3]
 We need wisdom, we need power
 True love for each other
 We have had so many big, but empty words
 So we come before Your face
 Asking for Your grace
 Bring Your people to a state of kingdom life
 Restore Your church again

[V4]
 Lord You see Your tired servants
 Your broken, wounded soldiers
 Oh how much we need Your precious, healing hand
 We need the power of the Cross
 As the only source for us
 When we stand up facing final battle cry
 Restore Your Bride again</lyrics>
<title>Herre, møt Ditt folk</title>
</song>